Description: Dooney and Bourke purse, Large Essex.Such rare find in this size! As you know, the majority of vintage Dooney & Bourke bags are kinda small by modern standards, but not this one! This is a very roomy bag!LARGE ESSEX STYLE marked on the flap. Style Number is marked as A2204102. Proudly made in USA! Indestructible leather, ALL WEATHER LEATHER is marked on the leather in front, and on the hanging tag and on the duck! The purse has a good weight to it! Excellent leather body! Suede side of the leather used in interior.Brown with grey, taupe body, with bright stunning aged brown leather trim and strap. The silver hanging tag is attached on the side.6 silver legs on the bottom to keep it clean.Adjustable strap will let you wear it as a shoulder bag as well as crossbody, messenger bag.Flap front, with pull thru silver ring strap for closure, extra flat pocket with the snap on the back.Hanging wall pocket inside. Tag and style number inside, the tag is cut.Duck on the main front flap is oversided and very bright. Measures 8" tall, 5" wide and 11" long, with long adjustable strap - 19" drop at longest as shown, can be shortened or made longer. In excellent condition for such age vintage bag, no odors or hardware issues.Slight rubbing on brown leather trim, the flap has pen marks on the inside.
